  "content": "<div><tt><br></tt></div>\n<div><tt>---</tt></div>\n<div><tt><br></tt></div>\n<div><tt>### I. | PRIMARY MANDATE</tt></div>\n<div><tt><br></tt></div>\n<div><tt>Combine every layer built so far:</tt></div>\n<div><tt><br></tt></div>\n<div><tt>- Project Names  </tt></div>\n<div><tt>- Artist IDs  </tt></div>\n<div><tt>- Logic Modes  </tt></div>\n<div><tt>- Business Containers  </tt></div>\n<div><tt>- Symbolic Logic  </tt></div>\n<div><tt>- Output Types  </tt></div>\n<div><tt>- Archive Systems  </tt></div>\n<div><tt>- Educational Capabilities  </tt></div>\n<div><tt>- Translation Tools  </tt></div>\n<div><tt>- Cross-Disciplinary Potential</tt></div>\n<div><tt><br></tt></div>\n<div><tt>Each entity will be recursively tagged, annotated, and structured for:</tt></div>\n<div><tt>- Iteration</tt></div>\n<div><tt>- Commercialization</tt></div>\n<div><tt>- Teaching</tt></div>\n<div><tt>- Remix</tt></div>\n<div><tt>- Myth-making</tt></div>\n<div><tt><br></tt></div>\n<div><tt>---</tt></div>\n<div><tt><br></tt></div>\n<div><tt>### II. | EXPANSION STRATEGY</tt></div>\n<div><tt><br></tt></div>\n<div><tt>Each node (project, artist ID, tool) will be expanded using deep prompts focused on:</tt></div>\n<div><tt><br></tt></div>\n<div><tt>- Origin Story / Context  </tt></div>",
